The structure of a value is kept opaque for performance reasons; setting
 and getting a value must be done through macros provided by 
\emph on
morpho:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Initialize a 
\family typewriter
value
\family default
 with a literal.

\series default
